<td><a href="/wiki/Shamanism" title="Shamanism">Shamanism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Buddhism" title="Buddhism">Buddhism</a>, <a href="/wiki/Christianity" title="Christianity">Christianity</a>, others</td>
